        </item>
        <item>
            <title>华为组中国车企联盟，推动超快速充电技术发展</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/huawei-forms-automakers-union-to-promote-superfast-ev-charging/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-forms-automakers-union-to-promote-superfast-ev-charging</link>
